                  </persName>
            . I am servant to Mr. Stone, a pawnbroker in Oxford-street. On the 17th of April, about one or two o'clock, the handkerchief was pawned by the prisoner. I am sure of him.</p>
               <p>(Handkerchief produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18220417-223-person2007">
